name: Sure Bet Sherbet Fountain
description: Each fizzy, sweet-tart purchase enters you automatically into an annual lottery held by Miss Terri’s. What’s the prize? Well, it wouldn’t be fun if we told you, would it?*  *by purchasing this candy you agree to 1 non negotiable entry into the annual Sugar Bowl Lottery. Winning entrants are required by law to appear at the Miss Terri’s main factory on BonBon 26 on a date to be specified by the MTSSC Legal team. No unauthorized absences will be tolerated.
